strings.Value: "I don't know what I'm doing here... Let's get this over with quickly."
{n}Ekun nods at you. His face is softer and at the same time, more resolute than usual.{/n}
{n}Octavia looks at Ekun, biting her lip.{/n} "My condolences..."
{n}Jubilost opens his mouth for a moment, raises his finger... But then only sighs, nodding silently to Ekun.{/n}
{n}Tristian smiles sadly at Ekun, then speaks, his voice warm.{/n} "The darkest hours are before the sunrise. Hold on. Trust me, you will feel better."
{n}Jaethal looks around silently, her eyes avoiding Ekun.{/n}
{n}Shaking his head and sighing heavily, Ekun looks away from you.{/n}
{n}The ranger's dark eyes are directed your way.{/n}"You've come. Thank you."
{n}Linzi hides her eyes, enough to conceal tears â€” but her voice breaks.{/n} "W-we are with you, friend."
